== Usage

GET = see this README

POST = HTML output from the Pygments syntax highlighting library
  Provide "lang" and "code", for example:
  POST http://pygments.appspot.com?lang=ruby&code=<%= 'hello world'.capitalize %>

== About

This was created so that http://flowcoder.com could run on http://heroku.com

See also:
http://pygments.org/
http://appengine.google.com/
http://github.com/trevorturk/pygments
